text: Phryneta silacea is a species of beetle in the family Cerambycidae. It was described by Per Olof Christopher Aurivillius in 1907. It is known from Togo and Ghana.BioLib.cz - Phryneta silacea. Retrieved on 8 September 2014. ==References== Category:Lamiinae Category:Beetles described in 1907
title: Phryneta silacea
